  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "59966e8f122bca0011b63585",
      "text": "6分間文章術",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1503030931,
      "updated": 1503030940
    },
    {
      "id": "59966ea6aff09e0000a42a32",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/bf4795181e3fc7260dc55ad5a5f35206]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1503030950,
      "updated": 1503030950
    },
    {
      "id": "59966ea8aff09e0000a42a33",
      "text": "\t[Amazon http://amzn.to/2wfDNGU]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1503030952,
      "updated": 1503030980
    },
    {
      "id": "5ae42a03aff09e00000ba420",
      "text": " [中野 巧]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524902403,
      "updated": 1524902411
    },
    {
      "id": "5ae42a0baff09e00000ba421",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524902412,
      "updated": 1524902412
    },
    {
      "id": "59966ec5aff09e0000a42a34",
      "text": " 何が書きたいかではなく、読者が何を読みたいか",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1503030981,
      "updated": 1503030997
    },
    {
      "id": "59966ed5aff09e0000a42a35",
      "text": "\t付箋で書き出し法を行った後、整列して、それから文章を書くことを進めている",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1503030997,
      "updated": 1503150901
    },
    {
      "id": "5998433caff09e0000222b77",
      "text": " 書き出し法を行う際にテンプレートとなる質問を用意していることが特徴",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1503150909,
      "updated": 1520407891
    },
    {
      "id": "59984388aff09e0000f98fda",
      "text": "  つまり[リーン・キャンバス]などのような[テンプレート]によって言語化を促す方法論の一つ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1503150984,
      "updated": 1503151617
    },
    {
      "id": "5998446daff09e0000f98fdc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1503151213,
      "updated": 1503151213
    },
    {
      "id": "59984439aff09e0000f98fdb",
      "text": " 1: 文章を書くことで達成したいことは？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1503151161,
      "updated": 1503151259
    },
    {
      "id": "59984477aff09e0000f98fdd",
      "text": " 2: あなたの文章を読んでワクワクしている人は何と言っている？(セリフの想像)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1503151223,
      "updated": 1503151260
    },
    {
      "id": "5998448aaff09e0000f98fde",
      "text": " 3: 2のセリフを言っている人はどんなポジティブな気持ち？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1503151242,
      "updated": 1503151316
    },
    {
      "id": "599844a6aff09e0000f98fdf",
      "text": " 4: 3の気持ちになった結果、その人がどんな行動をとってほしい？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1503151271,
      "updated": 1503151288
    },
    {
      "id": "599844b8aff09e0000f98fe0",
      "text": " 5: 3の気持ちになったのは、あなたがどんな言葉を掛けたから？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1503151288,
      "updated": 1503151308
    },
    {
      "id": "599844cbaff09e0000f98fe1",
      "text": " 6: 3と真逆なネガティブな気持ちは？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1503151308,
      "updated": 1503151330
    },
    {
      "id": "599844e4aff09e0000f98fe2",
      "text": " 7: 6の気持ちの人は何と言いそう？(セリフの想像)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1503151333,
      "updated": 1503151351
    },
    {
      "id": "599844f7aff09e0000f98fe3",
      "text": " 8: そのネガティブな気持ちを作り出している背景は？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1503151351,
      "updated": 1503151366
    },
    {
      "id": "59984506aff09e0000f98fe4",
      "text": " 9: そのネガティブな状態を受け入れるためにどんな言葉を掛ける？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1503151366,
      "updated": 1503151405
    },
    {
      "id": "5998452daff09e0000f98fe5",
      "text": " 10: この文章のテーマを一言でいうと？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1503151406,
      "updated": 1503151414
    },
    {
      "id": "5998457aaff09e0000f98fe7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1503151482,
      "updated": 1503151482
    },
    {
      "id": "5ae42a1baff09e00000ba433",
      "text": " [エンパシーライティング]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524902427,
      "updated": 1524902428
    },
    {
      "id": "59984536aff09e0000f98fe6",
      "text": "  文章を書く際に、ポジティブなペルソナとネガティブな[ペルソナ]を想定することで、読者の[共感]を呼びやすい文章を作ろうという方法論。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1503151414,
      "updated": 1524902428
    },
    {
      "id": "5a9f955eaff09e000053a370",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1520407902,
      "updated": 1520407902
    },
    {
      "id": "59966e9caff09e0000a42a31",
      "text": "\t文章を書くというタスクは[あいまいで大きいタスク]なので「6分間」という[タイムボックス]で小さく刻むのは有用。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1503030940,
      "updated": 1520407942
    },
    {
      "id": "5a9f9564aff09e000053a371",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1520407909,
      "updated": 1520407909
    }
  ]
}